oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Letter from Charlie Shelton to Delores from Top Billing
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Shelton, Charles; Top Billing, Inc.;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Typed letter from Charles Shelton to Delores of Top Billing, Inc. letting them know that he is returning their check because Porter Wagoner has paid for the cards he's been using. Hatch also inquires when two of their other clients are going to pay off their accounts. He also thanks them for sending a new photo of Jim Ed Brown.
